title: Start of Game of Thrones
description: Game of Thrones premieres on HBO. Ned Stark is appointed Hand of the King.

title: Ned Stark's Execution
description: Ned Stark is executed, sparking the War of the Five Kings.

title: Battle of Blackwater
description: Stannis Baratheon attempts to take King's Landing, but is defeated by the Lannisters with the help of wildfire.

title: The Red Wedding
description: Robb Stark, his wife, his mother, and many of his bannermen are killed at the Red Wedding.

title: Joffrey's Death
description: King Joffrey Baratheon is poisoned at his own wedding feast.

title: Jon Snow's Death
description: Jon Snow is betrayed and killed by his own men at Castle Black.

title: Cersei Destroys the Sept
description: Cersei Lannister destroys the Sept of Baelor with wildfire, killing many of her enemies in King's Landing.

title: Night King Breaches the Wall
description: The Night King uses Viserion to breach the Wall, allowing the Army of the Dead to march south.

title: Sack of King's Landing
description: Daenerys Targaryen attacks King's Landing, resulting in the city's fall and Cersei's death.

title: End of Game of Thrones
description: Bran Stark is elected king, and Jon Snow kills Daenerys Targaryen. The series ends.
